    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique was designed by Tenshunreiken Zacki of the Hidden Cloud, to serve as a method of quick assassination or execution. Usage immediately surrounds your hand with a crackling, golden halo of energy. You may use this energy in two ways: Either to make an immediate touch attack (as part of the technique), or you may hold the charge for up to 1 round per level, and make a melee touch attack with it at a later time. Such an attack counts as armed, and so does not provoke attacks opportunity. Once the charge hits a creature, it dissipates.<br><br>A creature hit by the charge takes 2d6 piercing, electrical and sonic damage (each, 6d6 total), and the target must save against being @Condition[paralyzed]{paralyzed} for 1d3 rounds.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage of any one type by 1d6, up to 6d6 total damage per energy type. You cannot add more than 2 damage dice per 3 levels.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
